hopobject.body: Which team do you support? entocort drugs.com That army just killed the democracy progress, and how can they now give it a re-birth? It will take decades if ever for such a place to deal with democracy. With US supporting coups tacitly -as Obama’s Rice advises the Generals in Egypt- it is hard to see a positive outcome any time soon- just not feasible with the players involved and a denfranchised 51% of the population.
